| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2399 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f186e4a9-ae9f-52b5-ba6f-215563237d44"
